00:37:33,220 --> 00:37:33,950
Mo Xiao,

832
00:37:34,160 --> 00:37:35,520
you want to stop us?

833
00:37:36,220 --> 00:37:37,840
Just you alone?

834
00:37:38,020 --> 00:37:38,740
(Bless us with Fair Winds and Fruitful Rains)

835
00:38:16,930 --> 00:38:19,390
It's the Immortal Lord's divine technique.

836
00:38:45,030 --> 00:38:46,560
The Immortal Lord's spell is strong,

837
00:38:46,560 --> 00:38:47,920
and he will protect Fengdu City

838
00:38:47,920 --> 00:38:48,640
and keep us safe and sound.

839
00:38:48,640 --> 00:38:49,360
Indeed.

840
00:38:49,550 --> 00:38:50,640
Mo Xiao.

841
00:39:00,890 --> 00:39:02,800
We're going to spread demonic spirit into Fengdu City.

842
00:39:02,800 --> 00:39:04,370
No one can stop us.

843
00:39:20,320 --> 00:39:21,920
Why are there still Heavenly Demon Spirits here?

844
00:39:21,920 --> 00:39:24,850
Could it be that someone from Mount Suyu has arrived?

845
00:39:34,070 --> 00:39:35,270
It should be fine now.

846
00:39:38,560 --> 00:39:39,280
Lixue!

847
00:39:51,520 --> 00:39:52,720
Feng Lixue?

848
00:39:53,280 --> 00:39:55,880
She has already been driven off Mount Suyu by Chongguang.

849
00:39:55,880 --> 00:39:59,210
I never thought she would seek refuge with the Shushan Sect.

850
00:39:59,840 --> 00:40:00,560
Mo Xiao.

851
00:40:00,760 --> 00:40:01,440
Lixue.

852
00:40:01,560 --> 00:40:02,280
Why are you here?

853
00:40:02,280 --> 00:40:03,910
I didn't collude with the Seven Caves and Nine Netherworlds of the Demon Sect.

854
00:40:03,910 --> 00:40:05,680
I'm sincere about renouncing evil and returning to righteousness.

855
00:40:05,680 --> 00:40:07,740
I'm willing to pay any price for this.

856
00:40:08,000 --> 00:40:08,900
Chongguang gave instructions.

857
00:40:08,900 --> 00:40:10,180
Just don't hurt her.

858
00:40:10,280 --> 00:40:11,760
Our matter is urgent.

859
00:40:13,760 --> 00:40:14,640
No!

860
00:40:16,400 --> 00:40:17,280
Come back!

861
00:40:19,040 --> 00:40:21,770
This seems to be that girl from Tianxing Mansion.

862
00:40:39,320 --> 00:40:39,980
Chang Ming!

863
00:40:42,170 --> 00:40:43,770
Supreme Lord, what's wrong?

864
00:40:43,920 --> 00:40:45,800
What happened in Fengdu City tonight?

865
00:40:45,800 --> 00:40:47,090
Tonight is the Ghost Festival.

866
00:40:47,090 --> 00:40:47,710
Seven Caves and Nine Netherworlds

867
00:40:47,710 --> 00:40:49,510
are taking advantage of the peak of yin and yang spiritual flow

868
00:40:49,510 --> 00:40:51,470
to invade Fengdu City

869
00:40:51,490 --> 00:40:52,570
and sense the whereabouts of the Sacred Stone

870
00:40:52,570 --> 00:40:54,830
in order to take the Sacred Stone for you.

871
00:40:57,080 --> 00:40:58,810
What have they done to Lixue?

872
00:40:58,960 --> 00:40:59,720
Lixue?

873
00:41:00,800 --> 00:41:02,420
I told them

874
00:41:03,350 --> 00:41:05,080
not to touch her.

875
00:41:06,470 --> 00:41:07,360
Go quickly!

876
00:41:07,680 --> 00:41:08,200
Yes.

877
00:41:22,290 --> 00:41:23,180
The important matter takes priority.

878
00:41:23,180 --> 00:41:25,240
We can't worry about everything now.

879
00:41:31,610 --> 00:41:32,540
Lixue!

880
00:41:38,560 --> 00:41:39,280
No!

881
00:41:43,720 --> 00:41:44,950
No!

882
00:41:45,400 --> 00:41:46,850
Come back!

883
00:42:50,190 --> 00:42:50,830
Lixue.

884
00:43:16,760 --> 00:43:18,520
The demonic power has dissipated.

885
00:43:18,520 --> 00:43:19,880
Don't let our guard down.

886
00:43:19,880 --> 00:43:21,320
The sky lanterns will burn bright all night.

887
00:43:21,320 --> 00:43:22,200
We must hold our ground.
